    {
      "id": "nUELlT269cADphFocz6fd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 526,
      "y": 412,
      "width": 905.9593505859375,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 283662783,
      "version": 166,
      "versionNonce": 2003833471,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772368375252,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now you want to get data out for rizwan - hash(\"rizwan) = 7 and you get data from index7.\n\nSo this hash function is constant time operation as of O(1)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now you want to get data out for rizwan - hash(\"rizwan) = 7 and you get data from index7.\n\nSo this hash function is constant time operation as of O(1)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-N8dmyrbFtlBNg7TK91IW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 585,
      "y": 547,
      "width": 8,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1543086879,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1531107313,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772368450585,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1MSctHbeVsIGn8vFiyMIW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 529,
      "y": 518,
      "width": 862.8115844726562,
      "height": 90.00000000000003,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b40",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2045030865,
      "version": 179,
      "versionNonce": 706205247,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772368731739,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now lets assume hash is giving me the very big number and the size of array is 10. Here we will do \nhashing.\ne.g.\n  ",
      "fontSize": 18.000000000000007,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now lets assume hash is giving me the very big number and the size of array is 10. Here we will do \nhashing.\ne.g.\n  ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qlQ6I3fZqBsGXMvGAe0Tl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535.3101196289062,
      "y": 592.5,
      "width": 354.0941894531252,
      "height": 66.00000000000006,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b41",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1965343743,
      "version": 285,
      "versionNonce": 256692497,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772368963257,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "hash of \"rizwan\" -> 734985 \nhash of \"ali\" -> 381356\nhash of \"ruhul\" -> 278596",
      "fontSize": 17.600000000000016,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "hash of \"rizwan\" -> 734985 \nhash of \"ali\" -> 381356\nhash of \"ruhul\" -> 278596",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2KWpzDhoIpgUHnu9Z3u3G",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 533,
      "y": 665,
      "width": 734.07958984375,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b42",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 934434641,
      "version": 413,
      "versionNonce": 1305580977,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772369326316,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Here we will do hashing such that all the numbers should come less than 10.\nwhat we do here is take reminder of the number by 10 as \n734985 % 10 = 5\n\nhash of \"ali\" -> 381356 -> 381356 % 10 = 6\nhash of \"ruhul\" -> 278596 -> 278596 % 10 = 6\n\nHere we have a collision.\nThere are ways to deal with collisions.\n2 ways resolve the collision:\n1) Chaining\n2) Open addressing\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Here we will do hashing such that all the numbers should come less than 10.\nwhat we do here is take reminder of the number by 10 as \n734985 % 10 = 5\n\nhash of \"ali\" -> 381356 -> 381356 % 10 = 6\nhash of \"ruhul\" -> 278596 -> 278596 % 10 = 6\n\nHere we have a collision.\nThere are ways to deal with collisions.\n2 ways resolve the collision:\n1) Chaining\n2) Open addressing\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "B3IJ_ZWjsSSlAHGfKhvzm",
